Package com.g28.plager.Antlr.Parsers.CParser

Interface CListener

All Superinterfaces:
org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
public interface CListener extends org.antlr.v4.runtime.tree.ParseTreeListener
This interface defines a complete listener for a parse tree produced by CParser.
